Activ Solar to Invest $1.5 Billion in Ukraine, WirtschaftsBlatt Reports

-- B y   B o r i s   G r o e n d a h l
-- 
2011-05-05T05:12:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/activ-solar-to-invest-1-5-billion-in-ukraine-wirtschaftsblatt-reports.html
Activ Solar will invest 700 million
euros for further solar energy projects in Ukraine after having
bought and modernized a semiconductor plant for 300 million
euros, Austrian daily newspaper WirtschaftsBlatt reported.  WirtschaftsBlatt was quoting Kaveh Ertefai, the chief
executive officer of the Vienna-based company, in an interview.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Boris Groendahl at 
 bgroendahl@bloomberg.net  